---
title: "Batch Generation Sequence - Suburb Content Pipeline"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as SvelteKit UI
    participant API as Workers API
    participant D1 as D1 Database
    participant Claude as Claude AI API
    participant KV as KV Cache

    Note over User,KV: 1. Batch Setup
    User->>UI: Select template, site, upload suburb list
    UI->>API: POST /api/batch {template_id, site_id, suburbs[]}
    API->>D1: Load template sections + rules
    D1-->>API: Template definition
    API->>D1: Load CSS catalogue for site
    D1-->>API: Verified class list
    API->>D1: Create batch_jobs record (status: pending)
    loop For each suburb in list
        API->>D1: Create job record (status: pending)
    end
    D1-->>API: Job IDs created
    API-->>UI: Batch created, N jobs queued
    UI-->>User: Show batch dashboard

    Note over User,KV: 2. Sequential Processing
    loop For each pending job
        API->>D1: Pick next pending job, set status: processing
        D1-->>API: Job with suburb data

        Note over API: 3. Data Enrichment
        API->>D1: Fetch suburb_data record
        D1-->>API: Suburb details (postcode, region, landmarks)
        API->>API: Select variant per section (deterministic hash)

        Note over API,Claude: 4. AI Generation
        API->>API: Build prompt: template rules + CSS catalogue + suburb data + constraints
        API->>Claude: Send structured prompt
        Claude-->>API: Streamed HTML content

        Note over API: 5. Automated Validation
        API->>API: Check: no placeholder tokens
        API->>API: Check: suburb name present, no cross-contamination
        API->>API: Check: section structure matches template
        API->>KV: Validate CSS classes against catalogue
        KV-->>API: Class validation results
        API->>API: Check: HTML well-formedness

        alt Validation passes
            API->>D1: Store page + page_version (source: batch)
            API->>D1: Update job status: complete
        else Validation fails (retry <= 3)
            API->>Claude: Retry with adjusted prompt
            Claude-->>API: Revised HTML
        else Validation fails (retries exhausted)
            API->>D1: Update job status: failed + error_message
        end
    end

    API-->>UI: Batch processing complete
    UI-->>User: Show results summary

    Note over User,KV: 6. Review Gate
    User->>UI: Open batch review dashboard
    UI->>D1: Fetch all generated pages for batch
    D1-->>UI: Pages with status indicators

    loop For each generated page
        User->>UI: Preview page in iframe
        alt Approved
            User->>UI: Approve page
            UI->>D1: Update page status: approved
        else Needs edit
            User->>UI: Edit content or provide feedback
            UI->>API: Regenerate with feedback
            API->>Claude: Refine prompt
            Claude-->>API: Updated HTML
            API->>D1: Save new page_version (source: ai_refine)
        else Rejected
            User->>UI: Regenerate from scratch
            UI->>API: POST /api/generate {page_id, regenerate: true}
        end
    end

    Note over User,KV: 7. Batch Export
    User->>UI: Export approved pages
    UI->>API: POST /api/export/batch {page_ids[]}
    API->>D1: Fetch latest approved versions
    D1-->>API: HTML content per page
    API->>API: Final class validation on each page
    API-->>UI: Validated HTML bundle (zip or individual)
    UI-->>User: Copy to clipboard / download zip
